      <title>消息人士称，Cinven 将成为 Bridgepoint 维生素井的主要投资者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/cinven-to-become-lead-investor-in-bridgepoint-s-vitamin-well-sources-say</link>
